{"priority": "minor", "kind": "bug", "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "links": {"attachments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/602/attachments_page=1.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/602.json"}, "watch": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/602/watch"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/602/comments_page=1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/602/unsubscribing-then-destroying-a-subscriber"}, "vote": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/602/vote"}}, "reporter": {"display_name": "Brian Gerkey", "uuid": "{3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9/5fa9ec73-0fec-4860-a202-e34ae23b6a12/128"}}, "nickname": "Brian Gerkey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9"}, "title": "Unsubscribing then destroying a Subscriber causes problems", "component": {"name": "transport", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/components/122882.json"}}}, "votes": 0, "watches": 3, "content": {"raw": "Debugging a problem in the Gazebo/ROS laser plugin led to the observation that following code (approximately boiled down to a simple case, but tested like this) is unsafe:\r\n\r\n        gazebo::transport::SubscriberPtr sub;\r\n        sub = gazebo_node->Subscribe(\"foo\", &CallBack, this);\r\n        sub->Unsubcribe();\r\n        sub.reset();\r\n\r\nThis sequence can lead to a segmentation fault at Node.cc:198:\r\n\r\n        return iter->second.front()->GetMsgType();\r\n\r\nSeems like the problem is that the Subscriber destructor unconditionally calls Unsubscribe().\r\n", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Debugging a problem in the Gazebo/ROS laser plugin led to the observation that following code (approximately boiled down to a simple case, but tested like this) is unsafe:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>    <span class=\"nt\">gazebo</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">transport</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">SubscriberPtr</span> <span class=\"nt\">sub</span><span class=\"o\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">sub</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nt\">gazebo_node-</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"nt\">Subscribe</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;foo&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nt\">CallBack</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"nt\">this</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">sub-</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"nt\">Unsubcribe</span><span class=\"o\">();</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">sub</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nc\">reset</span><span class=\"o\">();</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>This sequence can lead to a segmentation fault at Node.cc:198:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>    return iter-&gt;second.front()-&gt;GetMsgType();\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>Seems like the problem is that the Subscriber destructor unconditionally calls Unsubscribe().</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "state": "closed", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-03-22T23:20:50.348520+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:44:10.020709+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 602}